<div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset; border-style: solid; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-color: #336699 ">
<div style="display: none;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><b>Discussion:</b><br />
<br />
<b>Wards</b> win games. Wards buyout should be <b>ALWAYS on cooldown.</b> BUY THEM, MH IS GOOD!<br />
Use the <b>wards</b> wisely but not with a waster attitude i.e. Having 2 wards sitting in your inventory is simply a waste (unless there is really no reason to use one on map at that moment) but having 1 ward sitting in your inventory is fine. Remember whenever you dropped 1 ward you need to utilize that vision for the next 6mins to make it worthwhile, otherwise just save the ward for later. <br />
<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px">
